Document: GPUParticlesCollisionSDF3D
Path: godot/classes/class_gpuparticlescollisionsdf3d.rst
Summary: Provides 3D GPU-based particle collision using Signed Distance Fields.

GPUParticlesCollisionSDF3D

Inherits: GPUParticlesCollision3D < Node < Object

This node implements 3D GPU-based particle collision using Signed Distance Fields (SDF). It allows particles to collide with custom 3D shapes defined by SDF data, offering more complex and performant collision scenarios compared to traditional bounding box or sphere methods. The collision behavior is controlled by the properties of this node and the SDF data it references.
